                             'Trapezik' 1.02

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Trapezik' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} in which you create trapezoidal
patterns by rotating diagonal bars between surrounding borders. When
diagonal bars are placed correctly, coloured trapezes will appear
between those bars.

  If that sounds simple, there's a little complication: when you
rotate a diagonal bar, another one may change. Can you create 52
trapezes (and 8 parallelograms) in the fewest moves possible?

  Have fun!

